## Description {#details}

This class helps to store information for accelerator entries.

It prepares accelerator info for the certain <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/die">DIE</a> and store it inside OutUnit.

Definition at line 24 of file <a href="/docs/api/files/lib/lib/dwarflinker/lib/dwarflinker/parallel/acceleratorrecordssaver-h">AcceleratorRecordsSaver.h</a>.
